{{Top|canon=Victory project}}
The '''Victor Initiative Project''' was a joint venture between [[Kuat Drive Yards/Legends|Kuat Drive Yards]] and [[Rendili StarDrive/Legends|Rendili StarDrive]] to design an enhanced [[Capital ship/Legends|capital ship]] during the early part of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. The new ship had been ordered by [[Republic High Command/Legends|Republic High Command]], and [[Walex Blissex/Legends|Walex Blissex]] was the project head.

It resulted in the design of the [[Victory I-class Star Destroyer/Legends|''Victory I''-class]] [[Star Destroyer/Legends|Star Destroyer]]. They were initially slated to enter use by [[19 BBY/Legends|19.6 BBY]], but due to the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Separatist]] victory at the [[Battle of Foerost (Clone Wars)|Battle of Foerost]], a group of early ships, the "[[Victory Fleet]]," were launched six months early.

